==English==
===Noun===
'''success'''
# the [[achievement]] of one's [[aim]] or [[goal]]. (''His third attempt to pass the entrance exam was a success.'')
# (''Business'') [[financial]] [[profitability]].
# a person who achieves his or her goals. (''Scholastically, he was a success.'')

